org.friendlysnmp.event

Interface FRestoreDefaultListener


  • public interface FRestoreDefaultListener
    Implement this interface and register it with FScalar object to receive event to restore default value. This event is a result of this scalar value deletion from persistent storage.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.8 $
    See Also:
    FScalar

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void restoreDefault(FRestoreDefaultEvent ev)
      Register object of this class with FScalar or FTable node to receive event on removing persistency entry for this node in the MIB browser or setVolatile(true) method call.
